 <abstract><para>為開發潛力本土觀賞花卉及蕨類，以提供產業利用，本計畫將進行具有懸垂觀賞特性之垂枝石松、長葉腎蕨或東方狗脊蕨的體外大量增殖，及快速整齊育苗的技術的研探，並對具有花卉觀賞潛力之華八仙，進行選優之種質蒐集，並就選定之品系進行固定繁殖。
To develop potential endemic ornamental flower and fern for industryutilization, this program would study on the in vitro propagation and
fast neat seedling growing technology for Lycopodium phlegmaria L, Nephrolepis biserrata (Sw.) Schott, or Woodwardia prolifera Hook. ＆Arn with ornamental suspending characteristics. Collection for better mother stock and fix propagation for chosen lines for Hydrangea chinensis Maxim with flower ornamental potential are also included in this program.</para>
</abstract>
